    "collapsible_content_P3dQNR": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_W33Cm7": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What’s included in the 100-day pilot?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>1. Comprehensive health assessment – one of the most detailed on the market, covering lifestyle, stress, sleep, movement, nutrition and more to flag potential risks early.<br/>2. Blood test – a deep dive into 29+ biomarkers that give us a clear picture of your current health.<br/>3. Doctor review to interpret your results.<br/>4. Personalised longevity plan designed around your results.<br/>5. 8 coaching sessions over 100 days to keep you on track.<br/>6. Access to our easy-to-use app where your plan, results, and updates all live.<br/>7. A supportive community of like-minded members.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_gQPAgY": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How does the health assessment work?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>You’ll complete an in-depth health and lifestyle review covering:<br/>1. Sleep quality<br/>2. Stress and recovery<br/>3. Nutrition and hydration<br/>4. Movement and physical activity<br/>5. Daily habits and wellbeing<br/>This gives one of the most comprehensive pictures of your overall health available today.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_j9pqPY": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Which blood markers do you test for?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Our lab analysis covers 29+ key markers specifically chosen by our doctors, covering inflammation, iron, kidney, heart, liver, hormones and vitamins. These include:<br/>1. Inflammation<br/>- CRP<br/>2. Iron Status<br/>- Iron, T.I.B.C, UIBC, Transferrin Saturation, Ferritin<br/>3. Kidney Function<br/>-Urea, Creatinine, eGFR<br/>4. Cholesterol & Heart Health<br/>- Total Cholesterol, Triglycerides, HDL Cholesterol, HDL % of Total, LDL Cholesterol, Non-HDL Cholesterol<br/>5. Protein & Nutrition<br/>- Total Protein, Albumin, Globulin<br/>6. Liver Function<br/>- Alkaline Phosphatase, Alanine Transferase (ALT), Aspartate Transferase (AST), Gamma GT, Bilirubin<br/>7. Vitamins & Hormones<br/>- Vitamin B12, Vitamin D, TSH, FT4, FT3<br/>8. Blood Sugar<br/>- HbA1c<br/>These markers give a comprehensive snapshot of your health, helping us catch potential problems early and build your personalised longevity plan.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_6LMk8N": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Who will I work with?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>1. A doctor to interpret your test results and health assessment, and flag any early warning signs.<br/>2. A coach to translate those insights into practical steps, guiding you through 8 sessions across the 100-day pilot.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_bqnFC9": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What’s this app about?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Your personal dashboard:<br/>1. All your health data in one secure place.<br/>2. Updates from your doctor & coach.<br/>3. Your evolving longevity plan, always at your fingertips.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_cNDVLT": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is the Longevity Plan?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Think of it as your health roadmap. It’s personalised, practical, and updated as you go. It covers nutrition, movement, recovery, mindset, and more — everything you need to build a healthier, longer life.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_rhjmWr": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How interactive is the programme?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Very! You’ll get:<br/>1. A doctor review of your healthcare questionnaire and blood biomarkers at the start.<br/>2. 8 coaching sessions (1:1 or group) across 100 days.<br/>3. Weekly check-ins and progress reviews.<br/>4. Ongoing updates via the app.<br/>5. A community cheering you on.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_HEbgBT": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How is this different from a health MOT?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>Most MOTs stop at the test. We don’t. We give you: <br/>✅ A holistic and detailed lifestyle & wellness assessment.<br/>✅ A full biomarker blood test (29+ markers).<br/>✅ A personalised doctor led longevity plan.<br/>✅ 8 coaching sessions to put it into action.<br/>✅ An app that grows with you.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_TMH9x7": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What if I change my mind?",
            "icon": "none",
            "row_content": "<p>No stress. We offer a 100% money-back guarantee if you withdraw within 14 days.<br/>👉 Note: if the blood test kit has already been issued, that portion isn’t refundable (the labs don’t work for free!).</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
